cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.MM, cs.DC 

This paper deals with rate allocation in a heterogeneous network with LTE and 802.11 cells, which is a topic related to network infrastructure and communication systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves optimization problems, which could fall under cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.SY (Systems and Control). Additionally, the paper discusses path diversity, which could be related to multimedia systems (cs.MM) or distributed computing (cs.DC).
